<!DOCTYPE html>

<html>
    <head>
        <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:ital,wght@0,100;0,300;0,400;0,500;0,700;0,900;1,100;1,300;1,400;1,500;1,700;1,900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
        <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons" rel="stylesheet">


        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/report.css">

        <title>Relatório Kit Merenda - {{dataReport[dataReport.length - 1].report}}</title>             
        
    </head>
    {# onload="window.print()" #}
    <body onload="window.print()">
        <header>
            <div class="container">
                <div class="logo">
                    <a href="/">
                        <img src="/images/logo-pq-5.png" alt="">
                    </a>  
                </div>
                <div class="title">
                    <h3>
                        Relatório Kit Merenda</br>
                        {{dataReport[dataReport.length - 1].report}}
                    </h3>
                </div>
            </div>
            
        </header>
        <section class="content container">
            
            <div class="sub-title">
                <h4>Quantitativo por Escola</h4>
            </div>            
            <div class="item">
                <table width="100%">
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th>Escola</th>
                            <th>Presencial</th>                            
                            <th>Híbrido</th>                              
                            <th>Remoto</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        {% for school in dataReport %}
                            <tr>
                                <td>{{ school.name }}</td>
                                <td>{{ school.total_present }}</td>
                                <td>{{ school.total_hybrid }}</td>
                                <td>{{ school.total_remote }}</td>
                            </tr>
                        {% endfor %}
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>

            <div class="sub-title">
                <h4>Observação</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="item">
                <p>
                OS QUANTITATIVOS DEMONSTRADOS NA COLUNA DE  HÍBRIDO E REMOTO SÃO APENAS DE ALUNOS QUE 
                OPTARAM PARA O RECEBIMENTO DO KIT MERENDA.
                </p><br/>
                <p>Relatório gerado  por {{user.name}} em {{dateNow}}.</p>
            </div>

        </section>
        <footer>
            <p>Av. Maestro Sansão, 236 - Centro, Muriaé/MG - 1º Andar - Tel.: (32) 3729-1233 - E-mail: educacao@muriae.mg.gov.br</p>
        </footer>

        <script src="/scripts.js"></script>
    </body>




</html>